FIn%2Bthe%2BMouth%2Bof%2BMadness.jpg&h=3fe66814&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://www.radiozero.cl/static/2016/06/the-shining.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.radiozero.cl%2Fstatic%2F2016%2F06%2Fthe-shining.jpg&h=017c0bd3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.extmovie.com/files/attach/images/135/822/102/024/670bfddaebaeee0d1e76daf81d1744d5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.extmovie.com%2Ffiles%2Fattach%2Fimages%2F135%2F822%2F102%2F024%2F670bfddaebaeee0d1e76daf81d1744d5.jpg&h=e413f2cc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/9/9a/The_Dark_Tower_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F9%2F9a%2FThe_Dark_Tower_Poster.jpg&h=d22264de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.劇情是說約翰［John Trent］是名優秀的保險調查員兼自由作家，受出版社雇用調查知名恐怖小說家賽特凱恩［Sutter Cane］神秘失蹤的案件。凱恩的恐怖小說似乎具有能影響讀者的神秘魔力，甚至讓人做出瘋狂行為。約翰從賽特凱恩的小說中發現某些線索，可能指向凱恩躲藏的地點，於是他與女編輯琳達［Linda Styles］一同動身前往。向來鐵齒的約翰發現隨著路途他似乎與現實越來越遙遠，一步步進入了凱恩創造的惡夢&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n2.傑克&middot;托倫斯(Jack Torrance)是一名作家，為了擺脫工作上的失意，接受了一份在冬天維護科羅拉多州一家奢華的山間飯店的工作。他年幼的兒子擁有通靈能力，能夠看到過去和未來的東西，如棲息在飯店的鬼魂。到飯店安頓好後不久，這家人就被暴風雪困住了，傑克逐漸受到一個超自然的存在的影響；他陷入瘋狂並企圖謀殺他的妻子和兒子...<br />\n<br />\n3.1988年十月，緬因州德利鎮，結巴少年比爾&middot;丹柏因感冒在家休養時，為他的七歲弟弟喬治折一艘紙船。喬治穿黃色雨衣獨自在傾盆大雨的郊區中玩耍，但紙船卻被水沖入下水道裏。喬治前去查看時突然發現裏面有一個小丑，其自我介紹名叫「跳舞小丑潘尼懷斯」。潘尼懷斯通過紙船誘使喬治伸手進去拿，一瞬間張開血盆大口咬斷喬治的右手臂，最後將他拖入下水道裏消失無蹤<br />\n<br />\n4.故事發生在1989年夏季事件的27年後，魯蛇俱樂部成員已經長大並搬走了，直到一個不詳的電話把他們召回緬因州的德利鎮，對抗他們古老、會變形的敵人&mdash;跳舞小丑潘尼懷斯。 <br />\n<br />\n5.故事敘述在文明崩壞世界中，羅蘭&middot;德斯欽是名主要以雙左輪手槍為武器的僅存槍客，他希望能在宇宙的中樞「黑塔」找到阻止自己世界滅亡的方法<br />\n<br />\n8 15PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 註:閃靈 IT 黑魔塔同一世界 全部有關連<br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=Au6C6jYmoXJsWFOyr%2BboKD4xCSFqVWWaKp6LAuIW5iI%3D&h=d3d0e304\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=Au6C6jYmoXJsWFOyr%2BboKD4xCSFqVWWaKp6LAuIW5iI%3D&h=65e999b9\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"092cb1cc0326d6aa86cc2cf0a79d8bd018a5c276","tid":1648920,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T12:13:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd24f393645c4923a967ac7d064a177e3321ba84","tid":1648920,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T12:32:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be3dc6bfa474f4c3499b7fc18e35a7a15a73cfab","tid":1648920,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T13:16:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef500944fa02dbfda99da163d38820d7d2bec8c2","tid":1648920,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T13:56:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46a05c7c880856305235132e1ca9b95a6f34c501","tid":1648920,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T15:35:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angr